qoutes.Quote: The harder you work and the more you sear and bleed for a win
qoutes.Author: the sweeter that victory tastes.

qoutes.Quote: I train for two reasons. Number one
qoutes.Author: I love working out

qoutes.Quote: I always go heavy and I always go to failure. Even when I tell myself I'm gonna go easy
qoutes.Author: once I get to the gym and start working
qoutes.Category: I never end up going easy. I hate leaving the floor feeling like I could have done more weight or more reps. I just love working out and going further than I ever did before.

qoutes.Quote: It took me 20 years of hard training to get the physique I have today. what you need is what i had - BELIEF IN YOURSELF.
qoutes.Author: Branch Warren

qoutes.Quote: I would never have turned pro training like an average bodybuilder. There is no substitute for intensity.
qoutes.Author: Branch Warren

qoutes.Quote: I think that strength levels go hand in hand with building a great physique. You've got to lift heavy weight to get big - period.
qoutes.Author: Branch Warren
